params.markdown: This dashboard contains Elastic Load Balancing automatically distributes your incoming traffic across multiple targets, such as EC2 instances, containers, and IP addresses, in one or more Availability Zones. It monitors the health of its registered targets, and routes traffic only to the healthy targets.

embeddableConfig.description: The number of requests completed or connections made during the specified interval.
The number of connections that were not successfully established between the load balancer and the registered instances.
